'''異染色質'''（英語：'''Heterochromatin'''）是[[DNA|DNA]]內一種緊密組合的結構，[[轉錄|轉錄]]作用在其中受到限制。

==結構==
目前已知[[染色質|染色質]]有兩種類型，分別是[[真染色質|真染色質]]與'''異染色質'''<ref>
{{cite journal
| author = Elgin, S.C.
| title = Heterochromatin and gene regulation in ''Drosophila''
| year = 1996
| journal = [[Curr._Opin._Genet._Dev.|Curr. Opin. Genet. Dev.]]
| issn = 0959-437X
| volume = 6
| pages = 193-202
| doi=10.1016/S0959-437X(96)80050-5}}
</ref>。兩者差異最早是以受到染色之後的顏色深度來分辨，前者較淡，而後者，也就是異染色質則較深，可見其結構較為緊密（組蛋白包覆率及雙螺旋化的程度較較高）。異染色質一般分佈於細胞核的邊緣地帶。

異染色質大多是由不具遺傳活性的[[衛星DNA|衛星序列]]（satellite sequences）所構成<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Lohe, A.R., ''et al.''
| title = Mapping simple repeated DNA sequences in heterochromatin of ''Drosophila melanogaster''
| year = 1993
| journal = [[Genetics_(journal)|Genetics]]
| volume = 134
| issue = 4
| pages = 1149-1174
| issn = 0016-6731
| url = http://www.genetics.org/cgi/content/full/134/4/1149
| access-date = 2007-07-03
| archive-date = 2020-05-30
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200530143956/https://www.genetics.org/content/134/4/1149
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。其中的基因皆受到不同程度抑制，有些即使在真染色質內也無法表現<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Lu, B.Y., ''et al.''
| year = 2000
| title = Heterochromatin protein 1 is required for the normal expression of two heterochromatin genes in Drosophila
| journal = [[Genetics_(journal)|Genetics]]
| volume = 155
| issue = 2
| pages = 699-708
| url = http://www.genetics.org/cgi/content/full/155/2/699
| issn = 0016-6731
| access-date = 2007-07-03
| archive-date = 2009-03-02
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090302034439/http://www.genetics.org/cgi/content/full/155/2/699
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。在[[細胞週期|細胞週期]]的[[S期|S phase]]中，異染色質比真染色質更晚進行複製，且只在[[真核生物|真核生物]]中存在，[[著絲粒|著絲粒]]及[[端粒|端粒]]皆屬於異染色質，雌性體內去活化的[[X染色體|X染色體]]（也就是[[巴爾氏體|巴爾氏體]]）也是。

